review_blob: nice, nice nice. the aroma suggest a rich vinegar sour ale. the appearence is something to behold in a blonde, the flavor in right on with the aroma. comes on strong, with alight sour, vinegar taste. however the a rich creamy oliy texture takes you to a clean finish through and through. this is the ultimate good time brew. i rate this up with the likes of Duvel.
dark beer, mild flavor, malty with light molasses flavor. some orange and coriander initially. the honey tones out the bitterness of the the bok. but clean and crisp all the way through. very good!

rare brew, on paper this sounds so exciting, inovative, and fantastic. however a somewhat oily texture, vinegar perfumy aroma caught me off guard. appearence is perfetion, small head nice amber/orange hue that is slightly cloudy. the flavor falls flat, vinegar, bitter, and a short finish. dont mean to be harsh, but i  think i need to try again.

wow, wow, wow. the perfection of the dark ale. rich bold flavor of a stout, with the bitternessoftened with incredible vanilla, and enriched with oak. mixed in this complex bew are hues of coffe, and hopps. this is an awesome brew, so rich, enjoyable and easy drinking. i  plan to stock this brew as much as i can get.

dark cherry red, sweet molasses aroma. hoppy cherry flavo, rich creamy head, longlasting complex flavor with smooth finish. this is my staple beer, after a long had day, this is the way to relax!! simply awesome.
sweet caramel/banana aroma. light head, soft carbonation. dark lager with mild banana flavor. good novalty beer, not to be taken seriously.
rich easy drinking empirical stout ale. aged with oak, soft bitter coffey hue with soft woodzy flavor in the body. very satisfying
beer_name: Boulder Beer Obovoid Oak-Aged Oatmeal Stout

review_blob: strong coffey start, roasty, nutty flavor color black, a minimal head, lightly bitter, full body, creamy, soft carbonation with a lightly bitter finish. begin the day with a friendly brew, and enjoy with steak and eggs, have a sharp cheddar on the side
